revision.text:
{{ingredient}}

Almond Extract is the flavorful extract of the edible fruit of the Almond tree.

Almond is also the name of the edible and widely cultivated nut of this tree. Although popularly referred to as a nut, the almond fruit's seed is botanically not a true nut, but the seed of a drupe (a botanic name of a type of fruit).

